    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Anno incarnationis Iesu Christi millesimo centesimo tregesimo octavo,
                        indictione prima, die vigesimo quinto mensis februarii, apud <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches">Sancte Marie de Regione Turris</orgName>. Profiteor
                        ego <persName><name ref="Bonus">Bonus</name></persName> filius
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus de Pipignone">Petri de
                            Pipignone</name></persName> per hanc <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">libelli apparam</rs> quod tu
                        dominus <persName key="#Priests #Monks"><name ref="Wido Pomposianus"
                                >Guido</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> et <rs key="#Monks">monachus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Landed_possessions #Penalty #Maiores #Minores #Wine #Linen #Pigs #Books #Rent_in_kind #Rent_in_money #Exenia #Levies #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie in <placeName
                                ref="#places/4179"> Pomposia</placeName></orgName>, sub iure domini
                            <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/3747">Pauli</persName> vestri <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abatis</rs>, concessisti et confirmasti mihi meisque
                        filiis masculis, per libellum usque ad annos viginti novem ad renovandum,
                        totam illam <rs key="#Landed_possessions"> terram</rs> et <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vineam</rs>, quam ego habeo et teneo iure vestre ecclesie in <placeName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Landed_possessions #Penalty 
                            #Maiores #Minores #Wine #Linen #Pigs #Books #Rent_in_kind #Rent_in_money 
                            #Exenia #Levies"
                            ref="#places/4850">Ciriadi</placeName> et in <placeName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis 
                                #Landed_possessions #Penalty #Maiores #Minores #Wine #Linen #Pigs #Books 
                                #Rent_in_kind #Rent_in_money #Exenia #Levies"
                                ><geogName
                                key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Landed_possessions #Penalty 
                                    #Maiores #Minores #Wine #Linen #Pigs #Books #Rent_in_kind #Rent_in_money #Exenia #Levies"
                                ref="#estates/2430">Scanno</geogName></placeName>, <rs key="#Fines"
                            >territorio</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Fines" ref="#estates/2422"><placeName key="#Fines"
                                ref="#places/3515">Liviensi</placeName></geogName> et <rs
                            key="#Plebs">plebe</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Landed_possessions #Penalty #Maiores #Minores #Wine #Linen #Pigs #Books #Rent_in_kind #Rent_in_money #Exenia #Levies #Plebs"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3628">Sancti Mercurii</orgName>, cum omnibus
                        sibi partibus. Habendam, tenendam, laborandam, supersedendam et meliorandam;
                        sub <rs key="#Levies">terratico </rs>
                        <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores">maioris</rs> laboris quinto, <rs key="#Linen"
                            >lini</rs> septimo, <rs key="#Cereals #Minores">minuti</rs> octavo, anno
                        tercio arbor sit petenda semel reliquum sit mihi concessum; et omni anno in
                        festo sancti Martini <rs key="#Rent_in_money">tres denarios Lucenses</rs>
                        pro <rs key="#Pigs">porco</rs> et unum starium de <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Maiores">grano</rs> pro <rs key="#Exenia">exenio</rs>,
                        cum stario <placeName ref="#places/594">Ravenne</placeName>; pro quo
                        habeamus <rs key="#Size">mediam tornaturiam</rs> de supradicta terra pro <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">orto</rs> et area et tegete; in Pasca Domini
                            <rs key="#Rent_in_money">quinque denarios Lucenses</rs>; etdebeamus
                        portare terraticum vobis in civitatem Ravenne, ad <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/1480">Sancti Stefani
                            Maioris</orgName>. Auctorizare et defensare per te et per tuos
                        successores promisisti mihi meisque filiis masculis supradictam terram et
                        vineam. Calciarium <rs key="#Books">librum</rs> unum pro <rs key="#Price"
                            >tribus solidis denariorum Lucensium</rs>. Et det pars parti firmam
                        promissionem observandi hec supradicta, sub pena <rs key="#Penalty">unius
                            uncie auri</rs> et hac pena soluta hec locatio firma, ut superius
                        legitur, permanead. Scripta manu <persName key="#Notary"><name
                                ref="Bernardus">Bernardi</name></persName> divina clementia
                        Liviensis <rs key="#Notary">notarii</rs>. Albertucius …maramfus investitor,
                        Martinellus Frogobius, Amiconus, Ugo de Bona, Iohannes Ugoli de Girardo,
                        Iohannes de Ugone fuerunt huius locationis testes.</ab>
                </div>
